title: Bug 10593: Jar export does not add ".jar" suffix if not specified
description: When exporting files as a jar, if the jar name entered by the user does not already include the ".jar" suffix, the exported jar file is created without it.
SR: When exporting files as a jar, if the user enters a jar name without the ".jar" suffix, the jar export feature should automatically append the ".jar" suffix to the exported jar file name.
